title: Good way to waste time
text: This is my go to game to play when Iâ€™m sitting bored , my only real complaints about this game is itâ€™s unrealistic standard to progress,it takes forever to save up the money to play expensive games and your basically rigged to fail when you do get up there , I worked for weeks to get 1.2 million â€œdollarsâ€ on this game , went to play a single million â€œdollarâ€ game and got paired with a level 150 ( I was level 26) and lost every dollar . Which leads me into my second issue , there is absolutely no ranking in this game , you can be paired with literally any and every level , I played a tournament and I was the only low level there (Iâ€™ve never seen a person hit a 4 cusion pocket accurately until this tournament) . And I didnâ€™t even make it past the quarterfinals due to playing with people wayyyyyyyy out of my skill level , I feel they need to implement some kind of ranking system so the matches are more fairly based and more entertaining
